00:29:25.560 --> 00:29:29.260 align:middle line:84%
The true crisis in our world
is not social, political,

00:29:29.260 --> 00:29:32.180 align:middle line:90%
or economic.

00:29:32.180 --> 00:29:36.140 align:middle line:84%
Our crisis is a crisis of
consciousness and inability

00:29:36.140 --> 00:29:42.450 align:middle line:84%
to directly experience our
true nature, an inability

00:29:42.450 --> 00:29:45.630 align:middle line:84%
to recognize this nature in
everyone and in all things.

00:29:45.630 --> 00:29:53.510 align:middle line:90%


00:29:53.510 --> 00:29:56.210 align:middle line:84%
In the Buddhist
tradition, the bodhisattva

00:29:56.210 --> 00:30:00.250 align:middle line:84%
is a person with an
awakened Buddha nature.

00:30:00.250 --> 00:30:02.600 align:middle line:84%
A bodhisattva vows
to help to awaken

00:30:02.600 --> 00:30:06.280 align:middle line:84%
every being in the universe,
realizing that there

00:30:06.280 --> 00:30:09.130 align:middle line:90%
is only one consciousness.

00:30:09.130 --> 00:30:12.985 align:middle line:84%
To awaken one's true self,
one must awaken all beings.

00:30:12.985 --> 00:30:20.070 align:middle line:90%


00:30:20.070 --> 00:30:24.550 align:middle line:84%
There are innumerable sentient
beings in the universe.

00:30:24.550 --> 00:30:28.410 align:middle line:84%
I vow to help them
all to awaken.

00:30:28.410 --> 00:30:31.810 align:middle line:84%
My imperfections
are inexhaustible.

00:30:31.810 --> 00:30:35.420 align:middle line:90%
I vow to overcome them all.

00:30:35.420 --> 00:30:37.920 align:middle line:90%
The Dharma is unknowable.

00:30:37.920 --> 00:30:41.000 align:middle line:90%
I vow to know it.

00:30:41.000 --> 00:30:43.415 align:middle line:84%
The way of awakening
is unattainable.

00:30:43.415 --> 00:30:46.670 align:middle line:90%


00:30:46.670 --> 00:30:49.240 align:middle line:90%
I vow to attain it.

00:30:49.240 --> 00:31:00.822 align:middle line:90%